  :END:
 -  avoid estimating delta and using normal random variable?
For the bootstrap used in our Monte Carlo simulation, I realized that
we need to estimate delta--it wouldn't be fair to just use the true
delta--so I did. It works pretty well. It would be even cleaner if we
just resampled regression residuals, jointly with the AR(1)
innovations, instead of estimating delta and drawing from a normal
distribution.

